text: Schönefeld may refer to: ==Places in Germany== *Schönefeld, a municipality of Brandenburg near Berlin *Leipzig-Schönefeld, a quarter of Leipzig, Saxony *Schönefeld (Beelitz), a village in the town Beelitz, Brandenburg *Schönefeld (Niedergörsdorf), a village in the municipality Niedergörsdorf, Brandenburg *Schönefeld (Nuthe-Urstromtal), a village in the municipality Nuthe- Urstromtal, Brandenburg ==Transportation== *Berlin-Schönefeld Airport, one of Berlin's two main airports. *Berlin Schönefeld Flughafen station, the railway station of the airport *Autobahnkreuz Schönefeld, a German road interchange between the motorways A10, A13, A113 ==See also== *Schönfeld (disambiguation)
title: Schönefeld (disambiguation)
